<para>Use this to reduce the overhead of UI update events if your application has a lot of windows. If you set the value to -1 or greater than 0, you may also need to call <ref refid="classwx_window_1adf0a4987728bd0bf69f922641b3efbfc" kindref="member">wxWindow::UpdateWindowUI</ref> at appropriate points in your application, such as when a dialog is about to be shown. </para>
